				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13232372/scp-4863#post-4592079</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2020 00:51:27 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>NatVoltaic</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2800867</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's outside of the 93 Gly radius we can view of the universe from Earth, in a region of the cosmos whose light is never going to reach us; it's outside the observable universe.</p> <p>Fixed the missing words you pointed out</p> <p>EDIT: Added a short footnote that should clarify the observable universe bit.</p> 
				 	]]>
